SubjectRegulations Amending and Repealing Certain Canadian Food Inspection Agency Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending and Repealing CERTAIN CANADIAN FOOD INSPECTION AGENCY REGULATIONS (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) in order to (1) address requests from the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations to correct a number of discrepancies between official languages and make minor editorial modifications that were inadvertently missed when the provisions were originally published; and (2) repeal two spent regulations.
